Description: Read-only ReFS FUSE driver and progs,
 refs-fuse uses FUSE (Filesystem in Userspace) to provide support for the ReFS
 filesystem used by recent versions of Microsoft Windows.
 .
 The other refsprogs include 'refls', 'refcat', useful for listing and
 retrieving data from ReFS volumes, 'refsimage' for capturing an image of the
 ReFS filesystem and 'redb' / 'refsinfo' which allows access to the metadata
 of the filesystem for debugging and development.

